column2: SELECT TOP # e.SystemStudentID as StudentID, e.GradeLevel as EnrollmentGrade, e.SchoolYear4Digit as SchoolYear4Digit, # as Period, p.EventCategory as AssessmentSubject, # as MetricSource, # as MetricName, p.Hours as Score, p.EventDate as IsMostRecent FROM Enrollment as e JOIN ParentEngagement as p ON e.SystemStudentID = p.StudentID
